				<text x="80" y="42" text-anchor="middle" fill="#7c4dff" font-size="6" font-family="Quicksand, system-ui, sans-serif">agent</text>
				<text x="50" y="62" text-anchor="middle" fill="#9ca3af" font-size="5.5" font-family="Quicksand, system-ui, sans-serif" opacity="0.7">explicit control → latent agency → intentional behavior</text>
			</svg>
